attachmentHtml:
PC Number: 2013-1238

Date: 2013-11-07

 Sur recommandation du ministre de la Justice, le Comité du Conseil privé recommande que l’honorable Darin C. Chow, juge de la Cour provinciale de la Saskatchewan, soit nommé juge de la Cour du Banc de la Reine de la Saskatchewan.


 The Committee of the Privy Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Justice, advises that the Honourable Darin C. Chow, a Judge of the Provincial Court of Saskatchewan, be appointed a Judge of Her Majesty's Court of Queen's Bench for Saskatchewan.
